### Test Authentication API

### 1. Đăng nhập
POST https://localhost:7000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "emailOrEmployeeCode": "admin@company.com",
  "password": "admin123",
  "rememberMe": false
}

### 2. Đăng nhập với Remember Me
POST https://localhost:7000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "emailOrEmployeeCode": "employee@company.com",
  "password": "employee123",
  "rememberMe": true
}

### 3. Quên mật khẩu
POST https://localhost:7000/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "employee@company.com"
}

### 4. Đặt lại mật khẩu (sử dụng token từ email)
POST https://localhost:7000/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "employee@company.com",
  "token": "your-reset-token-here",
  "newPassword": "newpassword123",
  "confirmPassword": "newpassword123"
}

### 5. Đổi mật khẩu (yêu cầu đăng nhập)
POST https://localhost:7000/api/auth/change-password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "currentPassword": "oldpassword123",
  "newPassword": "newpassword123",
  "confirmPassword": "newpassword123"
}

### 6. Lấy thông tin user hiện tại
GET https://localhost:7000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 7. Đăng xuất
POST https://localhost:7000/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

"userId"

### ========================================
### Quản lý tài khoản (HR/Admin)
### ========================================

### 8. Tạo tài khoản cho nhân viên
POST https://localhost:7000/api/employeeaccount/create-account
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "employeeId": 1,
  "password": "initialpassword123",
  "role": "Employee"
}

### 9. Gán role cho nhân viên
POST https://localhost:7000/api/employeeaccount/assign-role
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "employeeId": 1,
  "role": "Manager"
}

### 10. Lấy danh sách nhân viên chưa có tài khoản
GET https://localhost:7000/api/employeeaccount/employees-without-account
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### 11. Lấy danh sách nhân viên đã có tài khoản
GET https://localhost:7000/api/employeeaccount/employees-with-account
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

